# Divs and admonitions

A plain div:

::: note
This is a generic note block. It can contain *any* djot.

Including multiple paragraphs.
:::

A warning:

::: warning
Watch out for null pointers.
:::

A tip:

::: tip
Use `array_map` for transformations.
:::

A caution:

::: caution
Destructive: cannot be undone.
:::

Nested div with class:

{.aside .small}
:::
A side note styled as small text.
:::

Block quote:

> "Premature optimization is the root of all evil."
>
> --- Donald Knuth

Block quote with caption:

> The only way to do great work is to love what you do.
^ Steve Jobs, Stanford 2005

Footnote reference[^note] in a sentence.

[^note]: Footnote definition body. Can wrap across lines
  with continuation indentation.
